YB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=87f19371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://warp.plus/LhMA</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T22:59:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Cloudflare WARP 不能隱藏你真 IP 地址　用家身份零保護</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/10/03/warpvpncaution/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F10%2F03%2Fwarpvpncaution%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3lQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=a2d206b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/10/03/warpvpncaution/tech-secure/</a><br />\n<br />\nWARP 自稱自己在定義上是一個「VPN」服務，但很多人預期 VPN 所提供的功能，例如<span style=\"color: red;\">最重要的隱身功能，如隱藏 IP 功能，WARP 就未能好好提供</span>，用戶要特別留意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Cloudflare WARP 不會對目標服務隱藏使用者的IP</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191004/60118170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191004%2F60118170&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3lQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=d98440f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191004%2F60118170&h=f5c59203\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191004/60118170</a><br />\n<br />\n有評測指出，WARP用的技術和傳統VPN不同，不會對目標服務隱藏使用者的IP，<span style=\"color: red;\">換句話說有可能不能突破地區限制的內容</span>，封網一樣死。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果記者用3個IP檢查網址做測試，包括：<a href=\"https://checkip.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcheckip.org&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3lQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=98906084\" target=\"_blank\">https://checkip.org</a>、<a href=\"https://whatismyipaddress.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwhatismyipaddress.com&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3lQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=0aa70059\" target=\"_blank\">https://whatismyipaddress.com</a>、<a href=\"https://nordvpn.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnordvpn.com&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3lQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=0110e2f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://nordvpn.com</a>。<span style=\"color: red;\">發覺WARP在後2個網址中出現了原本屬於香港的124字頭IP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</span>"}]}